@startuml
title UC-003 - Xuất hàng cho khách hàng

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Super Admin\n(`SUPER_ADMIN`)" as SA
actor "Warehouse Manager\n(`WAREHOUSE_MANAGER`)" as WM

rectangle "RFID Tracking System" {
  usecase "UC-003\nXuất hàng cho\nkhách hàng" as Main
  usecase "Tạo transfer\nWAREHOUSE_TO_CUSTOMER" as CreateOutbound
  usecase "Tự động COMPLETED" as AutoComplete
  usecase "Cập nhật Tag.status\n= COMPLETED" as UpdateStatus
  usecase "Ghi nhận destination\nHOTEL/RESORT/SPA/CUSTOMER" as SetDestination
}

SA --> Main
WM --> Main
SA --> CreateOutbound
WM --> CreateOutbound

Main .> CreateOutbound : <<include>>
Main .> AutoComplete : <<include>>
AutoComplete .> UpdateStatus : <<include>>
AutoComplete .> SetDestination : <<include>>

note right of AutoComplete
1-step workflow:
status = COMPLETED ngay khi create.
TransferItem.scannedAt cũng được set ngay.
end note

note bottom of Main
UC-003 chi the hien actor tao outbound:
SUPER_ADMIN va WAREHOUSE_MANAGER.
Neu can reverse sau khi COMPLETED,
source hien dung luong cancel rieng do ADMIN thuc hien.
end note

@enduml
